tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE CustomerOrders (
	order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	customer_name VARCHAR(255),
	order_date DATE,
	shipping_address VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(50),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES customers(customer_id)
);
